3     BIN_003   contractor99@yuvaext.com  BU_CONTENT_G4  CRITICAL   100.0    ESCALATE_IMMEDIATELY
```

## Next Steps

The entire data generation, clustering, behavioral enrichment, and inference architecture is now completely scalable. To move this closer to production, we would need to begin injecting **real DLP logs** into the pipeline, replacing our simulated analyst labels with actual historic ticket outcomes.
